  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rainze/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2715446-4.jpg" class="pil" alt="苏城" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/rainze/">苏城</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">专制皇权太霸道了，为了一句莫名的预言汉武帝就想杀掉所有姓魏的。李陵的人生太悲催，皇帝就是想弄死他。这部打着科幻旗号的小说只有后面几页体现了科幻。其实是一部历史架空小说。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/152044576/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u152044576-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="Michael Clemens" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/152044576/">Michael Clemens</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月19日          想读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/14355410/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u14355410-10.jpg" class="pil" alt="一棵白菜" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/14355410/">一棵白菜</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月18日          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:历史 科幻</span><br />

